text: Another Silent Hill game, another awesome soundtrack by Yamaoka. This is one of the first PS2 games I played, and what a game. James' journey through the foggy town is one of the most memorable and surreal in a video game, with a perfect balance between gameplay and story sequences that sometimes give me Twin Peaks vibes. The rusty and disjointed world is spot on. A masterpiece.
